The paper deals with medical image registration using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of a multi-agent system and Markov Decision Process (MDP) also suggests relevance to robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the application of the proposed method to medical imaging data suggests relevance to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
